Barbara Kent https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Kent 0 Barbara Kent (born Barbara Cloutman, December 16, 1907 – October 13, 2011) was an American film actress, prominent from the silent film era to the early talkies of the 1920s and 1930s, and a former (1925) Miss Hollywood.
